*************************************************************************
* >ReadMe file for Zap.Modules directory				*
*************************************************************************

This directory contains extensions and additions to Zap.

They are loaded when Zap needs them.

Please read the !Help file in each application to find out the features
provided and how to use them.

Thanks are due to everyone who has created extension modules for Zap for the
effort they have put in.

Authors names and addresses...
------------------------------

(Some of these might be out of date by now ...)

